在PL/Python中，防御来自<function>PyCObject_AsVoidPtr</>和
<function>PyCObject_FromVoidPtr</>的空指针结果 (Peter Eisentraut)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve <filename>contrib/dblink</>'s handling of tables containing
