运行8.2.X的用户不需要转储/恢复。不过，如果你是从一个早于8.2.14的版本升级而来，
那么请查看<xref linkend="release-8-2-14">。
</para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Add new configuration parameter <varname>ssl_renegotiation_limit</> to
      control how often we do session key renegotiation for an SSL connection
      (Magnus)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
添加新的配置参数<varname>ssl_renegotiation_limit</>，
控制多久为SSL连接做一次会话秘钥协商 (Magnus)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This can be set to zero to disable renegotiation completely, which may
      be required if a broken SSL library is used.  In particular, some
      vendors are shipping stopgap patches for CVE-2009-3555 that cause
      renegotiation attempts to fail.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
可以设置为0来完全禁用重新协商，如果使用了一个破损的库的话是需要这样的。
特别的，一些供应商为CVE-2009-3555提供了紧急补丁，引起重新协商的尝试失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible deadlock during backend startup (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复后端启动期间可能的死锁 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crashes due to not handling errors during relcache reload
      cleanly (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复由于relcache重新干净的加载期间没有处理错误引起的可能的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crashes when trying to recover from a failure in
      subtransaction start (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复在子事务启动中尝试从一个错误中恢复时可能的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix server memory leak associated with use of savepoints and a client
      encoding different from server's encoding (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复几个与使用保存点和客户端编码与服务器编码不同有关的内存泄露 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect WAL data emitted during end-of-recovery cleanup of a GIST
      index page split (Yoichi Hirai)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复GIST索引页分裂的最后恢复清理期间不正确的WAL数据发出 (Yoichi Hirai)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This would result in index corruption, or even more likely an error
      during WAL replay, if we were unlucky enough to crash during
      end-of-recovery cleanup after having completed an incomplete GIST
      insertion.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这会导致索引损坏，更甚至可能在WAL重放期间的一个错误，
如果我们很不幸的在完成一个不完整的GIST插入之后最后恢复清理期间崩溃。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make <function>substring()</> for <type>bit</> types treat any negative
      length as meaning <quote>all the rest of the string</> (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让<function>substring()</>对待所有<type>bit</>类型的负的长度为
<quote>所有剩余的字符串</> (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The previous coding treated only -1 that way, and would produce an
      invalid result value for other negative values, possibly leading to
      a crash (CVE-2010-0442).
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
以前的代码只以这种方式对待-1，并且会为其他负值产生一个无效的结果值，
可能导致崩溃 (CVE-2010-0442)。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix integer-to-bit-string conversions to handle the first fractional
      byte correctly when the output bit width is wider than the given
      integer by something other than a multiple of 8 bits (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复整数到位字符串的转换，当输出位的宽度比给出的整数宽，不同于8位的倍数时，
正确的处理第一部分的字节 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix some cases of pathologically slow regular expression matching (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复正则表达式匹配病理上缓慢的一些情况 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix the <literal>STOP WAL LOCATION</> entry in backup history files to
      report the next WAL segment's name when the end location is exactly at a
      segment boundary (Itagaki Takahiro)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复后端历史文件中的<literal>STOP WAL LOCATION</>项，
当结束位置正好是一个段的边缘时，报告下一个WAL段的名字 (Itagaki Takahiro)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix some more cases of temporary-file leakage (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复更多情况下临时文件的泄露 (Heikki)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This corrects a problem introduced in the previous minor release.
      One case that failed is when a plpgsql function returning set is
      called within another function's exception handler.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这纠正了一个在以前的小版本中引入的问题。
失败的一个情况是plpgsql函数的返回集在另一个函数的异常处理中调用时。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve constraint exclusion processing of boolean-variable cases,
      in particular make it possible to exclude a partition that has a
      <quote>bool_column = false</> constraint (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改善约束排除处理布尔变量的情况，特别的，让他有可能排除一个有
<quote>bool_column = false</>约束的分区 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      When reading <filename>pg_hba.conf</> and related files, do not treat
      <literal>@something</> as a file inclusion request if the <literal>@</>
      appears inside quote marks; also, never treat <literal>@</> by itself
      as a file inclusion request (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当读取<filename>pg_hba.conf</>和相关的文件时，如果<literal>@</>出现在双引号标记内部，
那么就不将<literal>@something</>看做一个文件包含请求；另外，
永不将<literal>@</>本身看做一个文件包含请求 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This prevents erratic behavior if a role or database name starts with
      <literal>@</>.  If you need to include a file whose path name
      contains spaces, you can still do so, but you must write
      <literal>@"/path to/file"</> rather than putting the quotes around
      the whole construct.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这阻止了角色或数据库名以<literal>@</>开头时的古怪行为。
如果你需要包括路径名包含空格的文件，你仍然可以这样做，但是必须写
<literal>@"/path to/file"</>而不是让双引号包含整个构造。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent infinite loop on some platforms if a directory is named as
      an inclusion target in <filename>pg_hba.conf</> and related files
      (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
如果一个路径被命名为<filename>pg_hba.conf</>和相关文件中的包含目标，
那么阻止某些平台上的无限循环 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible infinite loop if <function>SSL_read</> or
      <function>SSL_write</> fails without setting <varname>errno</> (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
如果<function>SSL_read</>或<function>SSL_write</>没有设置<varname>errno</>
而失败，则修复可能的无限循环 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This is reportedly possible with some Windows versions of
      <application>openssl</>.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
据报道，这在<application>openssl</>的某些Windows版本中是可能的。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>psql</>'s <literal>numericlocale</> option to not
      format strings it shouldn't in latex and troff output formats (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<application>psql</>的<literal>numericlocale</>选项，
不要格式化不应该是latex和troff输出格式的字符串 (Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make <application>psql</> return the correct exit status (3) when
      <literal>ON_ERROR_STOP</> and <literal>-&minus;single-transaction</> are
      both specified and an error occurs during the implied <command>COMMIT</>
      (Bruce)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当<literal>ON_ERROR_STOP</>和<literal>--single-transaction</>
都指定了并且一个错误发生在隐含的<command>COMMIT</>期间时，
让<application>psql</>返回正确的退出状态(3) (Bruce)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix plpgsql failure in one case where a composite column is set to NULL
      (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复一个复合字段设置为NULL情况下的plpgsql失败 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible failure when calling PL/Perl functions from PL/PerlU
      or vice versa (Tim Bunce)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复从PL/PerlU调用PL/Perl函数或反过来时可能的失败 (Tim Bunce)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Add <literal>volatile</> markings in PL/Python to avoid possible
      compiler-specific misbehavior (Zdenek Kotala)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
在PL/Python中添加<literal>volatile</>标记，避免可能的编译器具体的错误行为 (Zdenek Kotala)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure PL/Tcl initializes the Tcl interpreter fully (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保PL/Tcl完全初始化Tcl解释器 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The only known symptom of this oversight is that the Tcl
      <literal>clock</> command misbehaves if using Tcl 8.5 or later.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个疏忽唯一已知的症状是如果使用Tcl 8.5或更高版本，
Tcl <literal>clock</>命令错误行为。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent crash in <filename>contrib/dblink</> when too many key
      columns are specified to a <function>dblink_build_sql_*</> function
      (Rushabh Lathia, Joe Conway)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
阻止太多的关键字段指定到一个<function>dblink_build_sql_*</>函数时，
<filename>contrib/dblink</>中的崩溃 (Rushabh Lathia, Joe Conway)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix assorted crashes in <filename>contrib/xml2</> caused by sloppy
      memory management (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复由于粗心的内存管理引起的<filename>contrib/xml2</>中的各种崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make building of <filename>contrib/xml2</> more robust on Windows
      (Andrew)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让<filename>contrib/xml2</>的建立在Windows上更加稳健 (Andrew)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix race condition in Windows signal handling (Radu Ilie)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复Windows信号处理中的竞态条件 (Radu Ilie)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      One known symptom of this bug is that rows in <structname>pg_listener</>
      could be dropped under heavy load.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个错误一个已知的症状是<structname>pg_listener</>中的行在重负载的情况下会被删除。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2010e
      for DST law changes in Bangladesh, Chile, Fiji, Mexico, Paraguay, Samoa.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>版本2010e，
因为DST规律在Bangladesh、Chile、Fiji、Mexico、Paraguay、Samoa发生了改变。
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-8-2-15">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release 8.2.15</title>
