  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Migration to Version 8.2.12</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>迁移到版本 8.2.12</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 8.2.X.
    However, if you are upgrading from a version earlier than 8.2.11,
    see <xref linkend="release-8-2-11">.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
运行8.2.X的用户不需要转储/恢复。不过，如果你是从一个早于8.2.11的版本升级而来，
那么请查看<xref linkend="release-8-2-11">。
</para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve handling of URLs in <function>headline()</> function (Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改善<function>headline()</>函数中URL的处理 (Teodor)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve handling of overlength headlines in <function>headline()</>
      function (Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改善<function>headline()</>函数中超长标题的处理 (Teodor)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent possible Assert failure or misconversion if an encoding
      conversion is created with the wrong conversion function for the
      specified pair of encodings (Tom, Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
如果一个编码转换是用错误的编码转换函数为指定的编码对创建的，
那么阻止可能的断言失败或错误转换 (Tom, Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible Assert failure if a statement executed in PL/pgSQL is
      rewritten into another kind of statement, for example if an
      <command>INSERT</> is rewritten into an <command>UPDATE</> (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
如果一个在PL/pgSQL中执行的语句被重写到另一个类型的语句，例如，如果一个<command>INSERT</>
被重写到一个<command>UPDATE</>，那么修复可能的断言失败 (Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure that a snapshot is available to datatype input functions (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保一个快照可以用于数据类型输入函数 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This primarily affects domains that are declared with <literal>CHECK</>
      constraints involving user-defined stable or immutable functions.  Such
      functions typically fail if no snapshot has been set.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这主要影响用包含用户定义的稳定或不变的函数的<literal>CHECK</>约束声明的域。
这样的函数通常在没有设置快照时失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make it safer for SPI-using functions to be used within datatype I/O;
      in particular, to be used in domain check constraints (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让使用了SPI的函数用于数据类型I/O中更加安全；特别的，用于域检查约束中 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Avoid unnecessary locking of small tables in <command>VACUUM</>
      (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
避免在<command>VACUUM</>中不必要的锁定小表 (Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix a problem that made <literal>UPDATE RETURNING tableoid</>
      return zero instead of the correct OID (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复一个使得<literal>UPDATE RETURNING tableoid</>返回0而不是正确的OID的问题 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix planner misestimation of selectivity when transitive equality
      is applied to an outer-join clause (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复传递平等应用到一个外连接子句时规划器对选择性的错误估计 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This could result in bad plans for queries like
      <literal>... from a left join b on a.a1 = b.b1 where a.a1 = 42 ...</>
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这会导致像<literal>... from a left join b on a.a1 = b.b1 where a.a1 = 42 ...</>
这样的查询的不好的规划
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve optimizer's handling of long <literal>IN</> lists (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改善优化器处理长的<literal>IN</>列表 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This change avoids wasting large amounts of time on such lists
      when constraint exclusion is enabled.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个修改避免了在启用约束排除时在这样的列表上浪费大量的时间。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure that the contents of a holdable cursor don't depend on the
      contents of TOAST tables (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保可持有游标的内容不依赖于TOAST表的内容 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Previously, large field values in a cursor result might be represented
      as TOAST pointers, which would fail if the referenced table got dropped
      before the cursor is read, or if the large value is deleted and then
      vacuumed away.  This cannot happen with an ordinary cursor,
      but it could with a cursor that is held past its creating transaction.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
以前，游标结果中大的字段值可能被表示为TOAST指针，如果引用表在该游标被读取之前被删除，
或者如果该大值被删除然后清理了，那么将会失败。普通游标不会发生这种情况，
但是在持有过去它创建的事务的游标中会发生。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix memory leak when a set-returning function is terminated without
      reading its whole result (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复设置返回函数还没有读取它的整个结果就被截断时的内存泄露 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <filename>contrib/dblink</>'s
      <function>dblink_get_result(text,bool)</> function (Joe)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<filename>contrib/dblink</>的<function>dblink_get_result(text,bool)</>函数 (Joe)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible garbage output from <filename>contrib/sslinfo</> functions
      (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复来自<filename>contrib/sslinfo</>函数的可能的垃圾输出 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>configure</> script to properly report failure when
      unable to obtain linkage information for PL/Perl (Andrew)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<application>configure</>脚本，当不能为PL/Perl获取连接信息时，正确的报告失败 (Andrew)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make all documentation reference <literal>pgsql-bugs</> and/or
      <literal>pgsql-hackers</> as appropriate, instead of the
      now-decommissioned <literal>pgsql-ports</> and <literal>pgsql-patches</>
      mailing lists (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
让所有文档适当的引用<literal>pgsql-bugs</>和/或<literal>pgsql-hackers</>，
而不是现在退役的<literal>pgsql-ports</>和<literal>pgsql-patches</>
邮件列表 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2009a (for
      Kathmandu and historical DST corrections in Switzerland, Cuba)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>版本2009a（因为Kathmandu和Switzerland、
Cuba中的历史DST纠正）
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-8-2-11">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release 8.2.11</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>版本 8.2.11</title>

  <formalpara>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<title>Release date:</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<title>发布日期：</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>2008-11-03</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>2008-11-03</para>
  </formalpara>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
   This release contains a variety of fixes from 8.2.10.
   For information about new features in the 8.2 major release, see
   <xref linkend="release-8-2">.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个版本包含各种自8.2.10以来的修复。关于8.2主版本的新特性信息，
请查看<xref linkend="release-8-2">。
</para>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Migration to Version 8.2.11</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>迁移到版本 8.2.11</title>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 8.2.X.
    However, if you are upgrading from a version earlier than 8.2.7,
    see <xref linkend="release-8-2-7">.  Also, if you were running a previous
    8.2.X release, it is recommended to <command>REINDEX</> all GiST
    indexes after the upgrade.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
运行8.2.X的用户不需要转储/恢复。不过，如果你是从一个早于8.2.7的版本升级而来，
那么请查看<xref linkend="release-8-2-7">。另外，如果你正在运行一个早于8.2.X的版本，
建议在升级之后<command>REINDEX</>所有GiST索引。
</para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix GiST index corruption due to marking the wrong index entry
      <quote>dead</> after a deletion (Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复由于在一个删除之后标记错误的索引项<quote>dead</>引起的GiST索引损坏 (Teodor)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This would result in index searches failing to find rows they
      should have found.  Corrupted indexes can be fixed with
      <command>REINDEX</>.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这会导致索引搜索未能找到它们应该找到的行。损坏的索引可以使用<command>REINDEX</>修复。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix backend crash when the client encoding cannot represent a localized
      error message (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复客户端编码不能表示本地化的错误消息时的后端崩溃 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      We have addressed similar issues before, but it would still fail if
      the <quote>character has no equivalent</> message itself couldn't
      be converted.  The fix is to disable localization and send the plain
      ASCII error message when we detect such a situation.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
之前我们解决过类似的问题，但是如果<quote>character has no equivalent</>
消息本身不能被转换的话它将仍然会失败。
该修复是在检测到这样的情况时禁用本地化并发送纯ASCII错误消息。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crash when deeply nested functions are invoked from
      a trigger (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复深层嵌套的函数在一个触发器中调用时，可能的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve optimization of <replaceable>expression</> <literal>IN</>
      (<replaceable>expression-list</>) queries (Tom, per an idea from Robert
      Haas)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改善<replaceable>expression</> <literal>IN</> (<replaceable>expression-list</>)
查询的优化 (Tom, per an idea from Robert Haas)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Cases in which there are query variables on the right-hand side had been
      handled less efficiently in 8.2.x and 8.3.x than in prior versions.
      The fix restores 8.1 behavior for such cases.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
查询变量在右侧的情况在8.2.X和8.3.X中的处理效率比在以前的版本中低。
该修复为这样的情况恢复了8.1的行为。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix mis-expansion of rule queries when a sub-<literal>SELECT</> appears
      in a function call in <literal>FROM</>,  a multi-row <literal>VALUES</>
      list, or a <literal>RETURNING</> list (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复子<literal>SELECT</>出现在<literal>FROM</>中的函数调用、
一个多行<literal>VALUES</>列表或一个<literal>RETURNING</>列表中时规则查询的错误扩展 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The usual symptom of this problem is an <quote>unrecognized node type</>
      error.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这个问题通常的症状是一个<quote>未识别的节点类型</>错误。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix memory leak during rescan of a hashed aggregation plan (Neil)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复重新扫描散列的聚合计划期间的内存泄露 (Neil)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure an error is reported when a newly-defined PL/pgSQL trigger
      function is invoked as a normal function (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保当一个新定义的PL/pgSQL触发器被当做普通函数调用时报告一个错误 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent possible collision of <structfield>relfilenode</> numbers
      when moving a table to another tablespace with <command>ALTER SET
      TABLESPACE</> (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当使用<command>ALTER SET TABLESPACE</>移动一个表到另一个表空间时，
阻止可能的<structfield>relfilenode</>编号冲突 (Heikki)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The command tried to re-use the existing filename, instead of
      picking one that is known unused in the destination directory.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
该命令尝试重新使用现有的文件名，而不是使用一个在目标目录中已知未使用的文件名。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect tsearch2 headline generation when single query
      item matches first word of text (Sushant Sinha)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复单个查询条目匹配文本的第一个单词时，不正确的tsearch2标题生成 (Sushant Sinha)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix improper display of fractional seconds in interval values when
      using a non-ISO datestyle in an <option>-&minus;enable-integer-datetimes</>
      build (Ron Mayer)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复在一个<option>--enable-integer-datetimes</>建立中使用一个非ISO日期类型时，
间隔值中分数秒的不正确的显示 (Ron Mayer)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <function>SPI_getvalue</> and <function>SPI_getbinval</>
      behave correctly when the passed tuple and tuple descriptor have
      different numbers of columns (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当传递的元组和元组描述符有不同的字段数时，确保<function>SPI_getvalue</>和
<function>SPI_getbinval</>正确的行为 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This situation is normal when a table has had columns added or removed,
      but these two functions didn't handle it properly.
      The only likely consequence is an incorrect error indication.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
当一个表有添加或删除的字段时，这个情况是正常的，但是这两个函数没有正确的处理。
唯一可能的后果是一个不正确的错误指示。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>ecpg</>'s parsing of <command>CREATE ROLE</> (Michael)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<application>ecpg</>对<command>CREATE ROLE</>的解析 (Michael)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix recent breakage of <literal>pg_ctl restart</> (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<literal>pg_ctl restart</>最近的破损 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <filename>pg_control</> is opened in binary mode
      (Itagaki Takahiro)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
确保<filename>pg_control</>是以二进制模式打开的 (Itagaki Takahiro)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      <application>pg_controldata</> and <application>pg_resetxlog</>
      did this incorrectly, and so could fail on Windows.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
<application>pg_controldata</>和<application>pg_resetxlog</>
没有正确的做到这点，因此在Windows上可能会失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2008i (for
      DST law changes in Argentina, Brazil, Mauritius, Syria)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>版本2008i
（因为DST规律在Argentina, Brazil, Mauritius, Syria发生了变化）
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-8-2-10">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release 8.2.10</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>版本 8.2.10</title>

  <formalpara>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<title>Release date:</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<title>发布日期：</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>2008-09-22</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>2008-09-22</para>
  </formalpara>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
