  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>修改列表</title>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Remove security vulnerabilities that allowed connected users
      to read backend memory (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
删除允许连接的用户读取后端内存的安全缺陷 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The vulnerabilities involve suppressing the normal check that a SQL
      function returns the data type it's declared to, and changing the
      data type of a table column (CVE-2007-0555, CVE-2007-0556).  These
      errors can easily be exploited to cause a backend crash, and in
      principle might be used to read database content that the user
      should not be able to access.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
该缺陷包括抑制SQL函数返回它声明的数据类型和修改表字段的数据类型的正常检查
(CVE-2007-0555, CVE-2007-0556)。这些错误可以很容易的被利用来导致一个后端崩溃，
并且原理上可能被用来读取该用户不应该能够访问的数据库内容。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix not-so-rare-anymore bug wherein btree index page splits could fail
      due to choosing an infeasible split point (Heikki Linnakangas)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复由于选择一个不可行的分裂点，btree索引页分裂可能失败的不那么罕见的错误 (Heikki Linnakangas)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix Borland C compile scripts (L Bayuk)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复Borland C编译脚本 (L Bayuk)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Properly handle <function>to_char('CC')</> for years ending in
      <literal>00</> (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
正确的处理以<literal>00</>结束的年的<function>to_char('CC')</> (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Year 2000 is in the twentieth century, not the twenty-first.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
2000年是二十世纪，而不是二十一世纪。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      <filename>/contrib/tsearch2</> localization improvements (Tatsuo, Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
<filename>/contrib/tsearch2</>本地化改善 (Tatsuo, Teodor)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect permission check in
      <literal>information_schema.key_column_usage</> view (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复<literal>information_schema.key_column_usage</>视图中不正确的权限检查 (Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The symptom is <quote>relation with OID nnnnn does not exist</> errors.
      To get this fix without using <command>initdb</>, use <command>CREATE OR
      REPLACE VIEW</> to install the corrected definition found in
      <filename>share/information_schema.sql</>.  Note you will need to do
      this in each database.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
症状是<quote>relation with OID nnnnn does not exist</>错误。要不使用<command>initdb</>
来修复这个错误，使用<command>CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW</>安装在
<filename>share/information_schema.sql</>中找到的正确的定义。
注意，你将需要在每个数据库中执行。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve <command>VACUUM</> performance for databases with many tables (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
为拥有许多表的数据库提高<command>VACUUM</>性能 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix for rare Assert() crash triggered by <literal>UNION</> (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复由<literal>UNION</>触发的罕见的Assert()崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix potentially incorrect results from index searches using
      <literal>ROW</> inequality conditions (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复使用<literal>ROW</>不平等条件的索引搜索中潜在的不正确的结果 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Tighten security of multi-byte character processing for UTF8 sequences
      over three bytes long (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
为超过三字节长度的UTF8序列加强多字节字符处理的安全 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix bogus <quote>permission denied</> failures occurring on Windows
      due to attempts to fsync already-deleted files (Magnus, Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复由于尝试同步早已删除的文件，在Windows上发生的假的<quote>没有权限</>失败 (Magnus, Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix bug that could cause the statistics collector
      to hang on Windows (Magnus)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复可能导致状态收集器在Windows上挂掉的错误 (Magnus)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This would in turn lead to autovacuum not working.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
这会反过来导致自动清理不工作。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crashes when an already-in-use PL/pgSQL function is
      updated (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复一个早已使用的PL/pgSQL函数被更新时可能的崩溃 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve PL/pgSQL handling of domain types (Sergiy Vyshnevetskiy, Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
改善PL/pgSQL对域类型的处理 (Sergiy Vyshnevetskiy, Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible errors in processing PL/pgSQL exception blocks (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
修复处理PL/pgSQL异常块中可能的错误 (Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

